Package: snapflex
Version: 0.2.0
Title: Flexdashboards for SNAP Data Sets
Description: Provides functions and templates for generating local flexdashboards showcasing and summarizing SNAP data sets as well as functions 
    for accessing existing popular SNAP flexdashboards hosted online. 'snapflex' is a member package in the SNAPverse collection of R packages.
